gov.nasa.jpf.symbc.string

Class SymbolicStringConstraintsGeneral

  • java.lang.Object
    • gov.nasa.jpf.symbc.string.SymbolicStringConstraintsGeneral

  • public class SymbolicStringConstraintsGeneral
extends java.lang.Object
    Main entry point for the symbolic string solver. The solving is split into six steps 1. Convert the constraints to a StringGraph (what this class does) 2. Preprocess the StringGraph (gov.nasa.jpf.symbc.string.graph.PreProcessGraph 3. Solve the integer constriants (only choco for now) 4. Solve the string constriants with automata/sat/cvc 5. if step 4 gives unsat, and there is more integer values that satisfy step 3, go to step 3 6. Translate the StringGraph to the original symbolic strings. Visit http://www1.sun.ac.za/redmine/projects/jpfbugs/issues to log bugs
